Phelps Dodge Corp said filed registration statement Securities Exchange Commission offering four mln depositary share .
Each depositary share represents one quarter share convertible exchange preference share .
The liquidation preference depositary share 50 dlrs .
Quarterly dividend preference share cumulative payable beginning July 1 , 1987 .
Proceeds used redeem outstanding five dlr convertible exchangeable preference share , repay bank debt general corporate purpose .
